Fri Oct 04 2019 Szymon Romik <szymon.romik@intel.com>

	* Version 0.9

	This release adjusts pmemkv-ruby to work with pmemkv 1.0 and provides
        CI machinery.

Fri Jun 28 2019 Szymon Romik <szymon.romik@intel.com>

	* Version 0.8

	This is the first official release of pmemkv-ruby project.

        It provides Ruby bindings to libpmemkv 0.8 with simplified API and not
        functionally equal to its native C/C++ counterpart.
